<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>英语-VICE</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 14:41:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>《寂静岭》重制版 2020 年恐怖游戏现已登陆 Nintendo Switch 2</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/2020-horror-game-from-silent-hill-remake-developer-out-now-on-nintendo-switch-2/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新的 Nintendo Switch 2 版本为游戏机库带来了一款标志性的赛博朋克风格的恐怖游戏。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/2020-horror-game-from-silent-hill-remake-developer-out-now-on-nintendo-switch-2/"&gt;《寂静岭》重制版开发者在 Nintendo Switch 2 上推出的 2020 年后恐怖游戏&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 14:32:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/2020-horror-game-from-silent-hill-remake-developer-out-now-on-nintendo-switch-2/</guid></item><item><title>据新泄露消息称《女神异闻录 6》的开发即将完成</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/persona-6-development-reportedly-almost-finished-according-to-new-leak/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;有关《女神异闻录 6》将于 2027 年发布的消息可能刚刚被该游戏的开发人员证实。据翻译称，P6 的开发实际上可能已接近完成。 《女神异闻录 6》的开发可能即将完成 这一最新谣言来自一位据报道参与《女神异闻录 6》工作的翻译。在 [...]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.vice.com/en/article/persona-6-development-reportedly-almost-finished-according-to-new-leak/"&gt;据 New Leak 报道，《女神异闻录 6》的开发工作即将完成，&lt;/a&gt;最早出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jun 2026 14:12:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/persona-6-development-reportedly-almost-finished-according-to-new-leak/</guid></item><item><title>漫威《蜘蛛侠 2》迎来惊喜更新，庆祝全新一天</title><link>https://www.vice.com/en/article/marvels-spider-man-2-gets-a-surprise-update-to-celebrate-brand-new-day/</link><description>&lt;p&g